        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1261",
        "content": "\"As a man looks across great lakes I have gazed into the days to be, and as the great flies come upon four wings of gauze to skim over blue waters, so have my dreams come sailing two by two out of the days to be.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
