        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1261",
        "content": "And it was on the morning of a festival and the King came robed in white, with all his prophets and his seers and magicians, all down the marble steps to bless the land and all that stood therein as far as the purple hills, because it was the morning of festival.",
